text: Provides snippet functionality of Volume VOP SOP.

The Volume Wrangle Core SOP provides a version of the Volume VOP
SOP with only the snippet functionality.  Since it does not contain
the child VOP network, it can simplify the loading of the file.  There
is no performance benefit to using this node and it exists only to be
used internally by the Volume Wrangle SOP.
